Interface SomeValueSnak

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Snak
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SomeValueSnakImpl

    public interface SomeValueSnak
extends Snak
    A SomeValueSnak represents the information that a given property has some value that is not speficied further. In modelling, this is normally used if the specific value is unknown.
